bullets: Maximize p3ht_content to ~100% and set all dopants (d2_content, d6_content, d8_content) near zero; pure P3HT always gives the highest conductivity.
Increase d8_content as much as possible; longer-chain dopant dominates transport and will outperform any combination rich in d2_content.
Equal parts d2_content, d6_content, and d8_content are universally optimal regardless of p3ht_content or total dopant level.
Once any dopant is added, more is always better; keep raising (d2_content + d6_content + d8_content) without concern for morphology or percolation.
d6_content has no role in conductivity; set d6_content to zero in all cases and only vary p3ht_content.
Conductivity monotonically increases with p3ht_content even if dopant levels fall; never reduce p3ht_content for any reason.
If d2_content helps, then d8_content at the same level must help equally; swap d2_content for d8_content one-to-one without performance loss.
Avoid mixing dopants; single-dopant recipes (only d8_content high) always outperform any d2/d6 co-doping strategy.
